在提供的代码示例中，虽然明确设置了WebClient.Encoding属性为GB2312，但UploadValues方法只将编码应用于响应体。要解决此问题，可以尝试创建自定义的WebClient类，覆写GetWebRequest方法，以更改HttpWebRequest的Content-Type（即来自服务器的请求的Content-Type）。

以下是使用自定义的WebClient类的示例：

```csharp
using System;
using System.Net;
using System.Collections.Specialized;

public class MyWebClient : WebClient
{
    protected override WebRequest GetWebRequest(Uri address)
    {
        WebRequest request = base.GetWebRequest(address);
        if (request is HttpWebRequest)
        {
            (request as HttpWebRequest).ContentType = "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=gb2312";
        }
        return request;
    }
}

class MyProgram
{
    static void Main(string[] args)
    {
        var webClient = new MyWebClient();
        webClient.Encoding = Encoding.GetEncoding("gb2312");
        var formData = new System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection()
        {
            { "name", "名字" }
        };
        byte[] responseBytes = webClient.UploadValues("/TQM/edit/sub.aspx", "POST", formData);
        string response = Encoding.GetEncoding("gb2312").GetString(responseBytes);
        Console.WriteLine(response);
    }
}
```

在此示例中，我们创建了一个继承自WebClient的MyWebClient类，覆写了GetWebRequest方法，并设置了HttpWebRequest实例的Content-Type为application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=gb2312。这应该解决请求体中中文字符的乱码问题。

